## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9b1-104">可能会很不方便重命名方法参数，以便向 WMI 客户端提供更多用户友好的名称。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9b1-104">It might be inconvenient to rename method parameters to present WMI clients with more user-friendly names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cf9b1-105">此属性允许您分配用户友好的 WMI 名称，同时保留现有内部命名约定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9b1-105">This attribute lets you assign user-friendly WMI names while retaining your existing internal naming conventions.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cf9b1-106">在以下示例中，该整数参数保持在内部，i，但将向 WMI 客户端公开为"值"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cf9b1-106">In the following example, the integer parameter remains i internally, but will be exposed as "The Value" to WMI clients.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementTask]  
static public int PrintValue([ManagementName("The Value")]int i)  
{  
   Console.WriteLine("The Value is {0:x}", i);  
   return i;  
}  
```
